text:
I need an extra set of eyes. I'm trying to create a two-column section with text and a button on the left and text on the right. I keep getting an error message, but I can't figure out what I'm missing.

```{% dnd_section %}
  {% dnd_column %}
    {% dnd_row %}
      {% dnd_module
        path="@HubSpot/rich_text"
      %}
      {% end_dnd_module %}
    {% end_dnd_row %}
    {% dnd_row %}
      {% dnd_module
        path="../modules/button"
      %}
      {% end_dnd_module %}
    {% end_dnd_row %}
  {% end_dnd_column %}  
  {% dnd_module
     path="@HubSpot/rich_text"
   %}
  {% end_dnd_module %}
{% end_dnd_section %}```

Hi
<@U01DFCAB60J>
, your  code is ok, but you didn't define width on both column and module, That's why you are getting error, use below code for the same:


{% dnd_section %}
  {% dnd_column
    width=6,
    offset=0
  %}
    {% dnd_row %}
      {% dnd_module
        path="@HubSpot/rich_text"
      %}
      {% end_dnd_module %}
    {% end_dnd_row %}
    {% dnd_row %}
      {% dnd_module
        path="../modules/button"
      %}
      {% end_dnd_module %}
    {% end_dnd_row %}
  {% end_dnd_column %}
  {% dnd_module
     path="@HubSpot/rich_text",
    width=6,
    offset=6
   %}
  {% end_dnd_module %}
{% end_dnd_section %}
